---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---
<Layout title="About" description="About Bizarre Lineage Wiki — a fan-made tools and guide site for the Roblox game Bizarre Lineage." canonicalPath="/about">
  <section class="section"><div class="container page-content">
    <h1>About Bizarre Lineage Wiki</h1>
    <p>This is a fan-made wiki and tools site for <strong>Bizarre Lineage</strong>, a JoJo's Bizarre Adventure-inspired RPG on Roblox.</p>
    <p>We provide tier lists, build guides, game data, and tools to help players make informed decisions about their Stands, Fighting Styles, and Sub-Abilities.</p>
    <h2>Disclaimer</h2>
    <p>This site is <strong>not affiliated</strong> with Roblox Corporation or the developers of Bizarre Lineage. All game data is compiled from public resources including the official Trello board and community contributions.</p>
    <p>All trademarks and copyrights belong to their respective owners.</p>
    <h2>Data Sources</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Official Bizarre Lineage Trello board</li>
      <li>Community wikis and player reports</li>
      <li>In-game testing and verification</li>
    </ul>
    <h2>Contact</h2>
    <p>For corrections, suggestions, or business inquiries, please reach out via email at <strong>contact@bizarre-lineage.com</strong>.</p>
  </div></section>
</Layout>
<style>
  .page-content { max-width: 680px; }
  h1 { font-size: 1.8rem; font-weight: 800; color: #fff; margin: 0 0 1rem; }
  h2 { font-size: 1.1rem; font-weight: 700; color: #e2e8f0; margin: 2rem 0 0.5rem; }
  p { color: #94a3b8; font-size: 0.9rem; line-height: 1.7; }
  p strong { color: #e2e8f0; }
  ul { padding-left: 1.2rem; } li { color: #94a3b8; font-size: 0.88rem; margin-bottom: 0.4rem; }
</style>
